<plot>Once three friends since childhood - oligarch "Lyah", scientist "Candle" and a former turner-traveler "Coca" - get together at Lyah's 45 years anniversary, so to speak, on the highest level. These three friends haven't seen each other for 15 years and they became quite different. Once when they were young, they had an idea to go down the Volga River on a raft. They leave everything, and secretly from everyone, drift away to their days of childhood full of adventures. Their wives, mistresses and guards rush after them...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?438044</url></doc>
